   "body" : "This PR's goals are\r\n\r\n-  to simplify the `mempool_package_limits.py` functional tests with usage of the MiniWallet.\r\n-  to make progress towards the removal of the `make_chain`, `create_child_with_parents` and `create_raw_chain` methods of `wallet.py` which are currently used only at `mempool_package_limits.py` and `rpc_packages.py` and their functionality can be replicated with the existing MiniWallet methods.\r\n\r\nFor the purpose of the aforementioned goals, a helper method `MiniWallet.send_self_transfer_chain` is introduced and method `bulk_transaction` has been simplified to match current usage in `mempool_package_limits.py`.",
